reviews.text: The drinks lacked alcohol, the food was average and is being prepared behind the bar where you can witness the Bartenders/cooks eat. It seems a little unprofessional. It was also a little expensive for the area

Here was really great bar for dinner or gathering. A place was convenient, clean and good feel. Service was nice, friendly staff and manner.
Foods were nice, all dishes we ordered were excellent. We highly recommended the smoke chicken with apple salad, slow cook chicken roulade spinach, cheddar cheese.

Quite a nice place to have a chill dinner and drinks with friends. Dinner are with nice quality, highly recommend to order the risotto to try, with deep tomato based flavour and fried with chicken and salami. The pizza is very crispy and with a very creamy cheese flavour. The bar area is chill to stay and have cocktails with friends as well, nice!
Quite a lively place with plenty of people. Good for for German Weiss, oder Weizen, Bier lovers: Paulaner, Edelweiß
Nice place for hang out with friends. The tapas food is great, I love the roasted sucking pig and the Signature Platter. First try the Banana Bread Beer, taste really great!

result.name: Channel 3 Tapas Bar and Restaurant

reviews.text:
有時平日真係好需要relax一下，於是放工就去咗太子，因為我知道太子後面有好多間酒吧可以坐下傾下計😍

今次就去咗一間西班牙酒吧🤗 原來呢間除咗係酒吧之外，仲係一間西班牙餐廳❤️ 坐底咗就即時送上Nut😌 西班牙餐廳就梗係有三角形薯片＋餐廳自制醬汁☺️ 酸酸甜甜好開胃😋慢慢食慢慢叫❤️

首先叫個Channel 3 公司沙律😊 
沙律菜都幾新鮮，最緊要係有餐廳自家醋😍有少少藍莓味💓

西班牙小食併盤前菜，配酒一流👍
辣腸片比較鹹配啤酒真係一絕😍
蕃薯條比較健康，但可以再脆一點
另外兩個波波初初以為係薯仔波波，點知一個係煙三文魚包水牛芝士💋另一個係炸芝士波波💓💓💓 愛芝士就一定要試下👍

蘑菇帕爾馬火腿Pizza
Pizza唔算厚，芝士配蘑菇再加帕爾馬火腿不過不失😊

慢煮芝士菠菜雞肉卷
因為係慢煮關係，所以雞肉仍然保留肉汁🥰而且雞肉卷都比較大件😁 其實都好飽肚啖啖肉😇

餐廳燈光少少暗，令人有一種舒服嘅感覺🥰雖然係酒吧，但一啲都唔嘈吵👍傾計好去處😎

Openrice @Chloe凱彤

The drinks lacked alcohol, the food was average and is being prepared behind the bar where you can witness the Bartenders/cooks eat. It seems a little unprofessional. It was also a little expensive for the area

Here was really great bar for dinner or gathering. A place was convenient, clean and good feel. Service was nice, friendly staff and manner.
Foods were nice, all dishes we ordered were excellent. We highly recommended the smoke chicken with apple salad, slow cook chicken roulade spinach, cheddar cheese.
4.5星。食物質素，服務，環境都頗好，只是比較貴。openrice說一百至二百，但我們最後每人吃了接近三百。
很好的一間酒吧，食物好味，員工態度親切。值得推薦！
